    "For instance, the integration with LLMs allows intelligent tutoring systems to understand students' questions and past performances better to provide students with more personalized learning support [3].",
    "Similarly, the potential practicality is also shown on chatbots.",
    "Taking Chat Generative Pre-trained Transformer (ChatGPT) as an example, its feature of conversational interaction means it can encourage users to raise following reactions, which enables learners to personalize the knowledge they gain and encourages them to think thoroughly [4].",
    "Moreover, LLMs demonstrate their potential abilities to assist language education and academic writing as powerful tools.",
    "They are already used in tasks such as creating questions, providing prompts, grading essays, and generating feedback [5].Since LLM tools like ChatGPT have opportunities for enhancing teaching and learning experiences, it is essential to analyze their potential applications and future development trends."
